      "content": "@everyone - With just under 3 days left until DRC clean GDS needs to be submitted for Run #2, it is looking like there may be a few spare silicon slots (some half & quarter sizes).\n\n***If*** you upload a design to https://platform.wafer.space that is 100% clean and submitted for manufacturing there is a **chance** you will have your project manufactured for free. The project **must** also be open source and publically available.",
