      "content": "@everyone The submission deadline has passed! \uD83C\uDF89\n\nCongratulations to everyone who submitted to wafer.space GF180MCU Run 2.\nIn the next step, we will prepare the reticle with the paid-for designs, and fill the remaining slots with selected open-source designs, and finally submit it to fabrication. We will post updates on this process.\n\nPlease do not make any more changes to your layouts at this point. However, please verify and update your project's description, visibility, repository link and license accordingly.",
